@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!-- Full-page green background box -->
<div class="container py-5" style="max-width: 900px; background-color: #d6eadf; border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">

    <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-5" style="color: #2d572c;">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <!-- Section cards remain same -->
    <div class="card mb-4 shadow rounded-4 p-4">
        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>AgroSansar is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our services.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4 shadow rounded-4 p-4">
        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, location, etc.</li>
            <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username, password, profile details.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you access and use AgroSansar, such as pages visited and time spent.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, operating system.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4 shadow rounded-4 p-4">
        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide and maintain services</li>
            <li>To improve user experience</li>
            <li>To send notifications, updates, and promotional materials (only if you opt-in)</li>
            <li>To ensure security and prevent fraudulent activities</li>
            <li>To comply with legal requirements</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4 shadow rounded-4 p-4">
        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>With service providers who help operate our platform (under confidentiality agreements)</li>
            <li>For legal compliance if required by law, regulation, or court order</li>
            <li>During a business transfer such as a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell your information.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4 shadow rounded-4 p-4">
        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">5. Data Security</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Encryption for sensitive information</li>
            <li>Secure servers and firewalls</li>
            <li>Regular security audits</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4 shadow rounded-4 p-4">
        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Access, update, or delete your personal data</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
            <li>Request a copy of the information we hold about you</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4 shadow rounded-4 p-4">
        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted here with an updated "Effective Date".</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4 shadow rounded-4 p-4">
        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:agroSansarInfo@gmail.com" style="color: #2d572c;">agroSansarInfo@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>

</div>

<style>
    h2 {
        color: #2d572c;
    }

    ul {
        padding-left: 1.25rem;
    }

    li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    a {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
</style>
